title: Physics Wallah IPO: Prateek Maheshwari says, "It’s about trust, not just capital"
content:
Physics Wallah co-founder Prateek Maheshwari announced that the edtech firm’s IPO will open on November 11 and list on November 18. He said the goal isn’t just fundraising but building a “larger reach, larger branding.” Going public, he added, will help boost parent and student trust in the Physics Wallah brand.
